		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Buffalo</placeName> <add>&#63;</add> <add>&#63;</add> <date>Tebetta 5613</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Revd Mr</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><addressee>Leeser</addressee> <placeName><hi rend="underline">Phila. Pa</hi></placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I find myself duty bound&#44; to address<lb/> a few lines to you&#44; on account of our Holy<lb/> Religion.  I heard this week&#44; that the Learned<lb/> <persName>Revd Mr R. J. F&#252;rstenthal</persName> from <placeName><hi rend="underline">Breslaw</hi></placeName>&#44; has trans&#8222;<lb/>lated&#44; the valuable Book&#44; <add>Hebrew</add>&#44; from the<lb/> Hebrew&#44; in the <hi rend="underline">High German Language</hi>.  I would<lb/> advise you&#44; to take upon you the<lb/> <hi rend="underline">Task</hi> and translate&#44; only the first<lb/> Chapter&#44; and I <add>am</add> certain <del>and</del> that such<lb/> small pamphlet&#44; will be taken by all our<lb/> Bretheren&#44; Israelites&#44; and Gentiles.</p>
				<p>on account of the <add>Hebrew</add> <sic>wich</sic> you <hi rend="underline">recd</hi><lb/> the letters from me&#44; you will be so good<lb/> could <del>have p</del> <add>&#63;</add>&#44; <sic>untill</sic> next month&#44;<lb/> because it will proved by a <hi rend="underline">Justice</hi> of<lb/> the <hi rend="underline">Peacex</hi>&#44; if such <hi rend="underline">Divorce</hi> was <hi rend="underline">given</hi>.  <persName>Mr <hi rend="underline">Noah</hi></persName> did not&#44; <sic>answers</sic> me at present&#44; if<lb/> he will take the <hi rend="underline">bible</hi> with English&#44; the spelling<lb/> Book He recd from <persName>Ignausse</persName>&#44; but with prayer<lb/> Books is He provided on both. <add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p>I recd <sic>a</sic> answer from <placeName>Mobile</placeName>&#44; very <hi rend="underline">favourable</hi><lb/> not as a <hi rend="underline">preacher</hi> <add>but</add> for some other <hi rend="underline">Branches</hi><lb/> in our Religion at present I have no more<lb/> to communicate to you</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">I Remain Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">your friend and <add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">I am <persName role="author">M. Plutery</persName></p>
				<p>my <sic>bes</sic> respet<add>&#63;</add> to the Mr</p>
				<p><persName>Joseph Ash</persName>&#44; <add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p>his families and<add>&#63;</add> relations</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><add>&#63;</add>my <sic>adress</sic> you</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">know</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Revd Mr</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">Editor of the Occi&#8222;</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">&#8222;dent.</p>
